<div class="content" name="Introduction" uuid="1e5603df-c19e-4b87-9fc7-4612ea456461"><p>The Central Access Policy Identifier (ID) Retrieval Protocol
enables an administrative tool to query the Central Access Policies (CAPs)
configured on a remote computer.</p><p>Sections 1.5, 1.8, 1.9, 2, and 3 of this specification are
normative. All other sections and examples in this specification are
informative.</p></div>